Package: turtlearena
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, turtlearena-data (>= DATA_VERSION)
Recommends: turtlearena-server, turtlearena-wiimote
Description: 3D Third-Person Action Game
 Turtle Arena is an free and open source 3D third person action game based on
 ioquake3. It is a free stand-alone game.
 .
 This package installs the Turtle Arena client.

Package: turtlearena-server
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, turtlearena-data (>= DATA_VERSION)
Description: Dedicated server for Turtle Arena
 Turtle Arena is an free and open source 3D third person action game based on
 ioquake3. It is a free stand-alone game.
 .
 This package installs the Turtle Arena dedicated server.
